Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:07.41,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,不行嘛 花崎君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.10,0:00:12.75,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,前阵子玩水之后还是第一次见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.83,0:00:18.75,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,和明智君吵架了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:21.29,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.82,0:00:23.20,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,二十面相…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.55,0:00:31.31,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,让你理解我说的话虽然容易
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.48,0:00:34.03,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,但那样就不好玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.69,0:00:39.87,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,陪我玩玩吧 花崎君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.93,0:01:00.73,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你说自从有了我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.03,0:01:04.23,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}若再变成一个人就无法生活
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.28,0:01:07.63,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你故意开着玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.33,0:01:13.43,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我说我可笑不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.63,0:01:16.63,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你什么也没回答 只是微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.73,0:01:25.13,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你望向窗外的脸庞 带着忧伤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.98,0:01:30.88,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我只属于你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.93,0:01:34.23,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}这听起来也许想台词
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.33,0:01:40.23,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}在漆黑的道路上奋力前奔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.38,0:01:41.73,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.83,0:01:46.63,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你小小的手里紧握这句话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.68,0:01:52.13,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}只是静静地微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.83,0:01:58.23,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你只是温柔地 静静地微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.64,0:02:17.77,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,真难的啊 你竟然会来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.71,0:02:20.72,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,叫我来的不是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.30,0:02:22.74,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,是我没错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.19,0:02:26.64,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,毕竟花崎被你无视了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.28,0:02:26.20,EpTitle,,0,0,0,,{\fad(420,420)}纯洁的天平
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.43,0:02:29.74,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,明明你平时都是秒答的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.89,0:02:32.00,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,那家伙怎么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.31,0:02:33.33,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,要谈什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.48,0:02:36.19,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,用那副腔调说话…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.89,0:02:38.49,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,山根？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.49,0:02:40.33,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,喂 山根！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.15,0:02:43.13,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,马上来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.98,0:02:46.31,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,委托的东西全都准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:48.85,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,钢丝和备用的水下炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.38,0:02:53.25,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,急救装置和改良版的光学迷彩的伞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.93,0:02:56.36,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,学长 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.00,0:02:57.81,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.78,0:03:00.79,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,骨架是碳化纤维
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.79,0:03:04.21,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,比之前要轻47%
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.21,0:03:05.08,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.54,0:03:07.16,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,反应好冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.82,0:03:13.16,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,换做花崎早就「呜咻 好轻啊」地欢呼了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.16,0:03:14.07,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.07,0:03:17.10,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,学长不是那种个性的人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.32,0:03:18.43,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,这些就是全部了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.43,0:03:20.62,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,嗯…还有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:26.72,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,吹眠瓦斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:29.04,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,可以用水分调节量度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.69,0:03:30.45,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.45,0:03:31.59,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,所以说好冷淡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.59,0:03:32.28,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.92,0:03:34.98,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,还没好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.63,0:03:45.53,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,说的真香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.92,0:03:52.76,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.15,0:04:01.10,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:05.80,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.25,0:04:08.45,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,味道如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.45,0:04:10.07,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,回答我的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:16.04,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,这个眼神 我并不讨厌哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.38,0:04:20.04,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,不过 还远远不够
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.80,0:04:28.49,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,你的表情还能更加完美吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.25,0:04:42.83,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,中村刑警还真厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:46.84,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,漂亮地错过了要点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.86,0:04:49.01,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,春哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.38,0:04:54.00,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,难道说 你放心了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.34,0:04:59.66,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,他可是求你「狠下心来杀了我」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.91,0:05:06.38,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,他明明已经无法恢复往日的荣光了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:08.15,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,都是你干的好事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:10.80,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,是你把春哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:14.08,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,向有困难的他伸出援手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.03,0:05:18.19,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,这有什么不对吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.19,0:05:19.37,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,废话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:22.41,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,跟明智君比呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:26.12,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,烦死了 闭上嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.12,0:05:27.39,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,你又如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.26,0:05:34.96,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,你不会想说自己是正义的一方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.89,0:05:43.43,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,她喜欢的颜色是黄色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:46.08,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,是个喜欢足球和弹珠的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.22,0:05:49.01,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,虎牙很可爱的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.86,0:05:51.59,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,年仅10岁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.78,0:05:55.79,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,这孩子本应该被提供肾脏的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.26,0:05:57.04,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:05:59.86,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,有那个设施提供
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.58,0:06:10.42,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,你至今为止夺取的生命推断为22人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.57,0:06:14.40,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,这之后还会越来越多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.58,0:06:21.18,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,但是…我…把那里面的人们都…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.01,0:06:23.99,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,救了那些人真的好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.56,0:06:27.07,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,比起你没能救助的孩子们来说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.59,0:06:28.73,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.14,0:06:29.77,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,你是好人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.18,0:06:33.12,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,还是坏人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.96,0:06:35.80,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:37.29,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,我不想听
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.09,0:06:39.37,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.13,0:06:45.31,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,你只想看到「你想看到的东西」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.40,0:06:48.85,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,快住口！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.56,0:06:54.50,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.95,0:06:57.02,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,我暂时离开工作岗位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:57.75,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.00,0:07:00.43,TricksterItalics,,0,0,0,,见不到小奈绪我会寂寞的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.51,0:07:03.08,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,要不是某人发冷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.08,0:07:05.51,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,本来可以不用射击犯人就解决的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.67,0:07:08.16,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,这还真对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.27,0:07:11.72,TricksterItalics,,0,0,0,,嘛 世界上鼎鼎大名的名侦探
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.72,0:07:13.31,TricksterItalics,,0,0,0,,就算不帮忙我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.31,0:07:15.15,TricksterItalics,,0,0,0,,估计也忙得不可开交了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.15,0:07:17.15,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,不用这么闹别扭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.15,0:07:18.36,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,只要小奈绪希望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.36,0:07:20.76,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,我随时都能对你质朴的胸部…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.88,0:07:21.57,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.12,0:07:23.19,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.67,0:07:24.78,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:28.05,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,废弃的情趣旅馆呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.39,0:07:30.31,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.14,0:07:33.60,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,拜托您了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:37.22,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,三两下搞定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.09,0:07:47.78,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,你还真是个可怜的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.86,0:07:48.89,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.05,0:07:52.49,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,我很清楚哦 那种无法被爱的心酸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.75,0:07:56.68,TricksterItalics,,0,0,0,,{\an8}让各位就等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.30,0:07:59.12,TricksterItalics,,0,0,0,,{\an8}请看这边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:03.01,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,{\an8}明天即将开业的le-wAqua
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.01,0:08:08.62,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,{\an8}是花崎集团值得纪念的第十个大型复合商业设施
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.56,0:08:11.13,TricksterOverlap,,0,0,0,,你是第一次看到父亲的笑容吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.93,0:08:12.89,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.07,0:08:16.51,TricksterItalics,,0,0,0,,{\an8}能否请教一下 本店所独有的卖点是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.71,0:08:19.05,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,安全性 吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:23.27,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,{\an8}是说设施里有最新型的警备机器人负责保安工作是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.27,0:08:24.63,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.02,0:08:27.85,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,{\an8}今年春天 经历日之本重工事件后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.85,0:08:30.88,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,{\an8}连警方都停止了对警备机器人的使用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:32.10,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,{\an8}关于这部分…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.18,0:08:36.04,TricksterItalics,,0,0,0,,那个机器人不管是制造商还是性能都相去甚远
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.18,0:08:38.02,TricksterItalics,,0,0,0,,根本无法相提并论
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.02,0:08:40.07,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,想不想听听看？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.07,0:08:40.91,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:45.53,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,现在你的父亲会说你些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.82,0:08:49.66,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,明明三十年前就已经关门了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.76,0:08:53.71,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,负责拆除的人们却相继都遭遇意外事故
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.82,0:08:57.09,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,最近好像甚至被妖化为灵异场所
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:08:58.92,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,所以委托人想让我们去抓幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:00.97,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,她希望我们能找到出事的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:03.43,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,让工程重新开工
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.61,0:09:07.10,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,所以说抓到幽灵不就完事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:08.41,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,太不科学了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.41,0:09:10.06,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,你说啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.13,0:09:12.40,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,不科学的家伙不就在你边上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.89,0:09:15.93,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,那个嘛 倒也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.88,0:09:21.14,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,好可怕 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:30.85,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,{\an8}那么 就以下一个问题来收尾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.12,0:09:33.54,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,{\an8}那边系红色领带的先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.30,0:09:38.34,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,会长有计划要和自己的家人一同游玩吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.75,0:09:42.65,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,{\an8}非常抱歉 对那方面内容进行提问有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.94,0:09:45.84,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,当然有计划啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.40,0:09:53.20,TricksterItalics,,0,0,0,,不过犬子近来忙于社团活动 没什么时间陪我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.37,0:09:58.83,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,大人们全都是骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.19,0:10:02.81,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,他根本不在乎你的死活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.46,0:10:05.20,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,我又无所谓…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.79,0:10:11.61,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,你真的和以前的我很像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:13.21,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.36,0:10:16.12,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,不管是父亲还是明智君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.12,0:10:19.02,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,你都希望他们能多关注自己
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.25,0:10:21.06,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,认同自己
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:26.40,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,你对他们的褒奖饥渴难耐了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.55,0:10:34.23,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,让你见识一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.02,0:10:41.89,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,我从明智君那里得到的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.22,0:10:47.18,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.31,0:10:49.13,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,有点过度保护了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:02.43,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,当肌肉的表面超过150赌时
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.43,0:11:04.70,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,就会引起美拉德反应
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.70,0:11:08.51,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,氨基酸和糖类结合产生香气
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.51,0:11:14.77,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,换言之 做菜就是连锁的化学反应
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.29,0:11:16.14,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,委托呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.64,0:11:20.51,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,啊 今天是小野吕的假日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.51,0:11:22.90,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,我也想让小哔波休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.13,0:11:24.10,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.10,0:11:28.07,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,不用担心 我们的团员都是一个健康共同体
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.07,0:11:30.66,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,小野吕都有喝酵素哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.08,0:11:33.76,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,还有要来之前先申请一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.76,0:11:34.65,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.65,0:11:38.05,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,嘛 胜田的饭菜都很和我胃口就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.33,0:11:39.29,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:41.29,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,诶 要走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:43.29,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,有什么事的话通知我一声
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.88,0:11:46.34,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,我也是原团员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.57,0:11:54.76,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,从以前开始 唯独奇怪的直觉特别好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.80,0:12:03.81,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.14,0:12:05.05,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:07.61,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,有了吗？ 幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.32,0:12:09.31,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.40,0:12:11.78,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,是吗 那就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.97,0:12:13.04,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,拜托我？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.01,0:12:16.53,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,你一个人的话干起活来比较轻松吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.70,0:12:18.07,TricksterItalics,,0,0,0,,想怠工吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.32,0:12:19.56,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,被说中了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.56,0:12:20.55,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.15,0:12:25.31,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,我是想让你一个人尽情大闹一场
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:35.01,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,这是从明智君哪里收到的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.12,0:12:47.40,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,我曾被这把枪杀过一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:54.50,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,嘛 杀个人对明智君来说简直易如反掌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.04,0:13:00.71,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,毕竟他早已杀人无数了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.58,0:13:06.82,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,他的事 你好像一无所知呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:12.70,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,这样下去的话连明智君都会抛弃你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.04,0:13:18.58,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,他时常渴望着名为刺激的快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.20,0:13:23.24,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,渴望又一个提供他玩弄于股掌 给予他刺激的玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.31,0:13:27.64,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,如今小林君出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:29.86,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,他对你又有什么渴求呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.72,0:13:33.87,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,他才不会考虑玩腻的玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.76,0:13:39.11,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,唯有刺激 才是他被称作明智小五郎的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.11,0:13:44.36,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,顺从自己的欲望必然会出现牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.56,0:13:48.66,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,快乐都是建立在牺牲的基础上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.11,0:13:54.38,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,为了让明智君的大脑被我所占据
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.78,0:13:57.56,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,哪怕多大的牺牲我都在所不惜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.47,0:14:04.06,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,不是被别人要求做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.51,0:14:08.28,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,你自己想做的事又是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.64,0:14:27.56,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.13,0:14:29.17,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,不准逃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.72,0:14:40.06,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,抓到幽灵了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.16,0:14:41.66,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:43.14,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.83,0:14:45.73,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.24,0:14:47.73,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.72,0:14:53.23,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,委托人也真是辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.98,0:14:55.70,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.97,0:14:59.21,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,啊 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.43,0:15:01.73,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,装作幽灵的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.37,0:15:07.48,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,枝型吊灯上装的电灯泡是2010年以后生产的LED
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.79,0:15:09.83,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,而这张照片里拍摄的大楼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.28,0:15:13.07,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,开张时间和奥运会相同在2020年
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.48,0:15:17.47,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,两者在这家旅馆营业期间都尚未存在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:22.65,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,是想借老师的名声来炒作话题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.79,0:15:26.43,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,嘛 拆除大楼也得花不少钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:29.83,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,真遗憾呢 不是幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.83,0:15:30.70,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.15,0:15:33.85,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,嘛 从正面进行突破的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.06,0:15:37.64,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,不论何事大多都微不足道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.78,0:15:39.42,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,真相就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.42,0:15:40.85,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,我拼尽全力了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.86,0:15:43.18,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,你应该懂得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.18,0:15:45.87,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,我为了活下去已经拼尽全力了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.02,0:15:50.31,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,探讨人生可不是侦探的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.91,0:16:05.57,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.57,0:16:08.40,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,好 那么委托解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.70,0:16:13.05,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,你在犹豫些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.56,0:16:21.92,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,害怕说出自己的欲望吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.10,0:16:26.14,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,不 不是的 我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.91,0:16:32.80,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,怎么样 小林
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:34.59,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,不久后就会出来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.69,0:16:35.42,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.30,0:16:38.67,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,说不定很适合当侦探呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.51,0:16:40.96,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,小林啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.67,0:16:43.65,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,是你们中最有天赋的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.89,0:16:45.25,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,在我之上吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.25,0:16:46.01,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.76,0:16:47.89,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,也在花崎之上吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.85,0:16:50.61,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,他可不是侦探
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.67,0:16:54.00,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.23,0:16:56.98,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,我已经感到厌烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.85,0:17:00.01,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,那家伙的愚蠢程度
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.28,0:17:01.66,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,你说厌烦了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.06,0:17:04.66,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,忘了他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.90,0:17:06.66,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:07.41,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.60,0:17:10.12,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,不要啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.79,0:17:26.77,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,就算他厌烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.24,0:17:28.84,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,也想继续当他的玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.84,0:17:30.34,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,这就是你的愿望吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:33.30,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,但是很可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.16,0:17:36.65,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,你越是这样缠着他不放
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.03,0:17:39.36,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,他就越觉得你无趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.36,0:17:42.88,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,明智君寻求着新的刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.32,0:17:46.12,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,我才不是玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.32,0:17:47.26,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:50.49,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,连玩具也算不上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.62,0:17:55.05,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,对明智君来说你就跟不存在一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.92,0:17:58.83,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,与其被他玩腻然后抛弃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.44,0:18:02.15,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,「早知道就把你当成玩具好了」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.28,0:18:05.86,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,你不想让明智君这么说吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:10.94,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,不想让他后悔这么对待你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:14.00,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,让他彻底崩坏吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:17.49,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,我再问一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.60,0:18:22.88,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,现在你在渴望着什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.23,0:18:32.37,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,效仿…明智君吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.75,0:18:34.87,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.99,0:18:37.09,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,闭嘴闭嘴闭嘴！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:40.07,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,我…我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.77,0:18:45.72,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.62,0:18:50.73,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,我才不是玩具！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.93,0:18:56.91,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.71,0:19:07.59,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,和你不一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.26,0:19:11.74,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,不一样！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.85,0:19:18.10,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,回去咯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.10,0:19:19.90,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,你骗人的吧 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.90,0:19:20.59,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:22.30,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,花崎的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.61,0:19:24.04,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,才没有骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.67,0:19:26.89,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,虽然只是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.33,0:19:31.94,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,是看他想不想回到我们这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.94,0:19:33.50,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,首先要从这点开始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.50,0:19:34.36,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,懂了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.18,0:19:43.32,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,你这家伙 还是一心想死吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.32,0:19:44.71,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,废话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:47.71,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,讨厌侦探的工作吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.71,0:19:49.06,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,井上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.06,0:19:50.06,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,并不讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.47,0:19:54.75,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,但是 反正这样的生活也不长久…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.75,0:19:56.62,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:19:59.49,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,你想在那之前死去 吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.18,0:20:11.46,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,我来的时候这个就…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.30,0:20:15.90,TricksterItalics,,0,0,0,,呀 明智君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.21,0:20:18.32,TricksterItalics,,0,0,0,,真是神清气爽的早晨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.34,0:20:22.19,TricksterItalics,,0,0,0,,我想到了能取悦你的游戏了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.15,0:20:29.67,TricksterItalics,,0,0,0,,花崎健介君他…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:32.57,TricksterItalics,,0,0,0,,就借给我保管咯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.78,0:20:37.54,TricksterItalics,,0,0,0,,这孩子相当有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.58,0:20:41.46,TricksterItalics,,0,0,0,,你想夺回他吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:43.43,TricksterItalics,,0,0,0,,还是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.59,0:20:50.67,TricksterItalics,,0,0,0,,你的玩具就任我处置了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.75,0:20:54.90,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.06,0:20:59.58,TricksterItalics,,0,0,0,,来 把我找出来然后逮捕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.57,0:21:06.50,TricksterItalics,,0,0,0,,事情变得有趣了呢 明智君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.81,0:21:11.13,TricksterItalics,,0,0,0,,你现在一定露出了相当不错的表情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.79,0:21:25.38,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,演的不错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.10,0:21:30.12,TricksterMain,,0,0,0,,这不挺能干的吗
